&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a class="toc-backref" href="https://jiaweizhuang.github.io/blog/personal-website-with-jupyter-support-using-nikola-and-github-page/#id3"&gt;3   Installation and initialization&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
